\n<Alyssa><Wrap>Who thought it was a good idea to rig so many mechanical traps and levers down here?
\n<Thomas><Wrap>Whoever it was, I am sure they are burning in a special pit in hell.

\n<Alyssa><Wrap>I haven't been through these parts, but others who've looked around here said there are some levers to open up the doorways. Those chuckleheads weren't particularly forthcoming with useful information.
\nr<Galathan><Wrap>Any idea where they are? Or how they work?
\n<Alyssa><Wrap>I think the levers are around the corner to the right, the doors to the left.
